<h1>PAD Reference</h1>

<p>Complete working examples for PAD template tags, properties, and pipe functions.</p>

<hr>

<h2>Tags ({$tagCount})</h2>
<p>Template tags control flow, data, and output. <a href="?fragments/claude/tags">View all tags &rarr;</a></p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
<tr style="background:#ccc;"><th>Tag</th><th>Description</th><th>Category</th></tr>
{tags}
  <tr{property:even} style="background:#f5f5f5"{/property:even}>
    <td><a href="?fragments/claude/tags/{$name}">{$name}</a></td>
    <td>{$desc}</td>
    <td><i>{$cat}</i></td>
  </tr>
{/tags}
</table>

<hr>

